      "date": "2012-10-30 19:31:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI suppose the same information is in commit message. \nIt fixes race in deadlock detection algorithm.\nif deadlock isn't detected it means client application will block forever.\nThe race can happen when 2 threads are trying to\ngrant 2 locks which deadlock on each other.",
